headline.print_headline: Malzahn: Johnson Will Start for Auburn at QB
headline.main: Malzahn: Johnson Will Start for Auburn at QB

lead_paragraph: Jeremy Johnson will be No. 6 Auburn's starting quarterback against Arkansas, and Nick Marshall will play in the game at some point.
